targeted rewrites.\",\"status\":\"draft\",\"detail\":null,\"started_at\":null,\"completed_at\":null,\"last_event_summary\":null,\"last_event_type\":null,\"last_event_at\":null},{\"stage\":\"audio\",\"label\":\"Audio\",\"description\":\"Configure narration settings and generate resumable audio artifacts.\",\"status\":\"draft\",\"detail\":null,\"started_at\":null,\"completed_at\":null,\"last_event_summary\":null,\"last_event_type\":null,\"last_event_at\":null},{\"stage\":\"finalize\",\"label\":\"Finalize\",\"description\":\"Read, listen, review final assets, and download exports.\",\"status\":\"draft\",\"detail\":null,\"started_at\":null,\"completed_at\":null,\"last_event_summary\":null,\"last_event_type\":null,\"last_event_at\":null}],\"story_brief\":{\"id\":\"cd7a500e-9177-42bf-a0b6-2faed3d22ffa\",\"revision_number\":1,\"story_idea\":\"A child and an otter guardian drift after runaway lanterns to bring each light home before the harbor sleeps.\",\"desired_themes\":\"Gentle courage, belonging, and a calm return home.\",\"key_images\":\"Floating lanterns, otter paws, quiet docks, and moonlit water.\",\"audience_notes\":\"Keep it cozy for a sensitive five-year-old who likes rescue stories without villains.\",\"must_have_elements\":\"End with the harbor settled, the lights restored, and the child tucked in safely.\",\"raw_brief\":\"A child and an otter guardian drift after runaway lanterns to bring each light home before the harbor sleeps.\\n\\nDesired themes: Gentle courage, belonging, and a calm return home.\\n\\nKey images: Floating lanterns, otter paws, quiet docks, and moonlit water.\\n\\nTarget audience notes: Keep it cozy for a sensitive five-year-old who likes rescue stories without villains.\\n\\nMust-have elements: End with the harbor settled, the lights restored, and the child tucked in safely.\",\"normalized_summary\":\"A child and an otter guardian in a harbor, aiming for belonging, gentle courage, a restful sense of safety, a safe return home. Recurring mo