{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The compose wrapper did stall exactly where expected, so I\u2019m bypassing that dependency bootstrap and executing the QA runner inside the already-running `browser` container. That keeps the verification inside the repo\u2019s intended harness w...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_242", "text": "The compose wrapper did stall exactly where expected, so I\u2019m bypassing that dependency bootstrap and executing the QA runner inside the already-running `browser` container. That keeps the verification inside the repo\u2019s intended harness without touching the broken backend startup path.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 468, "prompt_index": 44, "prompt_name": "43 \u2014 Normalize the User Brief Into Structured Preferences", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T20:45:07-07:00"}
