{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The browser assertions passed and both screenshots were written. I\u2019m opening the desktop and mobile captures once to confirm the interpretation panel is actually visible and not just present in DOM text, then I\u2019ll clean up the temporary...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_245", "text": "The browser assertions passed and both screenshots were written. I\u2019m opening the desktop and mobile captures once to confirm the interpretation panel is actually visible and not just present in DOM text, then I\u2019ll clean up the temporary QA specs, commit, and write the final reviewer summary.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 473, "prompt_index": 44, "prompt_name": "43 \u2014 Normalize the User Brief Into Structured Preferences", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T20:45:18-07:00"}
