{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The screenshots proved the route rendered, but the saved viewport crops before the new interpretation panel, so they\u2019re not good reviewer evidence yet. I\u2019m switching both captures to full-page screenshots and rerunning them so the actual...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_247", "text": "The screenshots proved the route rendered, but the saved viewport crops before the new interpretation panel, so they\u2019re not good reviewer evidence yet. I\u2019m switching both captures to full-page screenshots and rerunning them so the actual normalized brief UI is visible in the artifacts, not just asserted in DOM text.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 476, "prompt_index": 44, "prompt_name": "43 \u2014 Normalize the User Brief Into Structured Preferences", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T20:45:27-07:00"}
