{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The mobile focused capture is solid, but the desktop element crop came back narrower than the actual layout, so I\u2019m replacing it with an explicit clipped region based on the panel\u2019s bounding box. That should give one reviewer-friendly de...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_256", "text": "The mobile focused capture is solid, but the desktop element crop came back narrower than the actual layout, so I\u2019m replacing it with an explicit clipped region based on the panel\u2019s bounding box. That should give one reviewer-friendly desktop artifact that shows the interpretation form at a readable scale.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 492, "prompt_index": 44, "prompt_name": "43 \u2014 Normalize the User Brief Into Structured Preferences", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T20:47:00-07:00"}
{"color": "cyan", "emoji": "\ud83d\udee0", "event_type": "Command Started", "message": "in progress: /bin/zsh -lc \"docker exec storyteller-browser-1 /bin/sh -lc 'cd /workspace/tools/webapp-qa && node --input-type=module <<'\\\"'\\\"'EOF'\\\"'\\\"'\nimport fs from \\\"node:fs/promises\\\";\nimport puppeteer from \\\"puppeteer\\\";\n\nconst outputPath = \\\"/workspace/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-43-brief-panel-desktop.png\\\";\nawait fs.mkdir(\\\"/workspace/.artifacts/webapp-qa\\\", { recursive: true });\nconst browser = await puppeteer.launch({\n  executablePath: process.env.PUPPETEER_EXECUTABLE_PATH,\n  args: [\\\"--no-sandbox\\\", \\\"--disable-setuid-sandbox\\\"],\n  headless: true,\n});\ntry {\n  const page = await browser.newPage();\n  await page.setViewport({ width: 1440, height: 960 });\n  await page.goto(\\\"http://frontend:8566/sessions/b7725d68-5ab4-4516-a37c-4a9e5eb3ac1f?stage=brief\\\", { waitUntil: \\\"networkidle2\\\", timeout: 15000 });\n  await page.waitForFunction(() => document.body?.innerText.includes(\\\"Editable interpretation\\\"), { timeout: 15000 });\n  const rect = await page.\"'$eval(\".story-brief-stage__interpretation-panel\", (element) => {\n    const bounds = element.getBoundingClientRect();\n    return {\n      x: bounds.x + window.scrollX - 24,\n      y: bounds.y + window.scrollY - 24,\n      width: bounds.width + 48,\n      height: Math.min(bounds.height + 48, 1600),\n    };\n  });\n  await page.screenshot({\n    path: outputPath,\n    clip: {\n      x: Math.max(0, rect.x),\n      y: Math.max(0, rect.y),\n      width: Math.min(1440 - Math.max(0, rect.x), rect.width),\n      height: rect.height,\n    },\n  });\n  console.log(`Saved screenshot to ${outputPath}`);\n} finally {\n  await browser.close();\n}\nEOF'\"'\"", "raw_event": {"item": {"aggregated_output": "", "command": "/bin/zsh -lc \"docker exec storyteller-browser-1 /bin/sh -lc 'cd /workspace/tools/webapp-qa && node --input-type=module <<'\\\"'\\\"'EOF'\\\"'\\\"'\nimport fs fro