{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The desktop clip is still too narrow, likely because the panel\u2019s grid collapses into a thin bounding box when clipped directly. I\u2019m switching to the simpler, more reviewer-usable approach: scroll the interpretation panel into view and ca...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_260", "text": "The desktop clip is still too narrow, likely because the panel\u2019s grid collapses into a thin bounding box when clipped directly. I\u2019m switching to the simpler, more reviewer-usable approach: scroll the interpretation panel into view and capture the viewport at each size.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 499, "prompt_index": 44, "prompt_name": "43 \u2014 Normalize the User Brief Into Structured Preferences", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T20:47:34-07:00"}
